\frac{2-\sqrt{2+\sqrt3}}{\sqrt{2+\sqrt3}}=\frac{2-\sqrt{2+\sqrt3}}{\sqrt{2+\sqrt3}}\frac{\sqrt{2-\sqrt3}}{\sqrt{2-\sqrt3}}=\frac{2\sqrt{2-\sqrt3}-\sqrt{2+\sqrt3}\sqrt{2-\sqrt3}}{\sqrt{2+\sqrt3}\sqrt{2-\sqrt3}}=
=\frac{2\sqrt{2-\sqrt3}-\sqrt{(2+\sqrt3)(2-\sqrt3)}}{\sqrt{(2+\sqrt3)(2-\sqrt3)}}=\frac{2\sqrt{2-\sqrt3}-\sqrt{2^2-(\sqrt3)^2}}{\sqrt{2^2-(\sqrt3)^2}}=
=\frac{2\sqrt{2-\sqrt3}-\sqrt{4-3}}{\sqrt{4-3}}=\frac{2\sqrt{2-\sqrt3}-\sqrt{1}}{\sqrt{1}}=2\sqrt{2-\sqrt3}-1
